==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: People are not sages, who can be without error?

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén fēi shèng xían, shú néng wú gùo

===Proverb===
'''[[人]][[非]][[圣贤]]，[[孰]][[能]][[无]][[过]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Nobody's perfect.

===Alternate forms===
[[人]][[非]][[聖]][[賢]]，[[孰]][[能]][[無過]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])


===Related terms===
[[人]][[非]][[圣贤]]，[[谁]][[能]][[无过]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

[[人]][[非]][[聖賢]]，[[誰]][[能]][[無過]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

